{"id": 2578, "genre": 1001, "title": "你手机里那些装了却没用过的 app 都是怎么来的？", "description": "欢迎分享你那些从来没打开却一直没卸载的 app。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cifotart）", "record_count": 4471, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201810221425161UPE5tiGrJTohWVa.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-01T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 308224, "content": "Apple watch。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838601}, {"id": 308225, "content": "整理一下，发现自带的几乎都没有用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489908}, {"id": 308737, "content": "知乎上推荐的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481753}, {"id": 308738, "content": "系统自带或者是手机空间太大，有兴趣就下了，然后不用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492748}, {"id": 308227, "content": "笔记类的吧，安装了好久却很少去用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408012}, {"id": 308739, "content": "TED英语，这个学渣真的坚持不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421216}, {"id": 308484, "content": "下载了美颜相机，但却极少不自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490692}, {"id": 308229, "content": "修图软件？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489970}, {"id": 308485, "content": "基本不自拍的人下载美颜相机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490692}, {"id": 309765, "content": "好奇心日报。。每次发现有好几个月都没有用过了，想着要不就卸载吧，最后一次打开来看看是个什么，哈哈哈真有意思。然后又是几个月以后，诶？好奇心日报是干嘛用的，要不卸载吧，最后打开再看一眼吧………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116354}, {"id": 316421, "content": "认为对自己学习有用，想着以后会用得到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797157}, {"id": 308230, "content": "背单词学英语的app，下完就觉得自己用过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489977}, {"id": 308742, "content": "平安金管家，几乎没有打开过", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711752}, {"id": 308233, "content": "一时性起", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 308234, "content": "被人安利的各种app😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456423}, {"id": 308235, "content": "鸡肋 App 上排名 推荐", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483423}, {"id": 314379, "content": "苹果自带的\n还有一些新闻视野类的app，我以为我心怀天下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522158}, {"id": 308236, "content": "我以为自己26岁还是会好好学英语", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483423}, {"id": 308492, "content": "颜值", "image": "img/option/option/201811021840343ZKQcyPGDM9T8mNH.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156749}, {"id": 308237, "content": "界面新闻装了三年换了俩手机，唯一一条收藏还是三年前刚装的时候。反正手机数据迁移，不费事。跟好奇心差不多，删了觉得少个信息渠道，不删觉得占地。就留着吧，我这算站队吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033447}, {"id": 308238, "content": "自然是新手机迫不及待下载一大堆，过一段时间点击的时候才发现需要登录，然后因为麻烦卸载。至此，一部分APP没跟我正式见面就被pass", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462141}, {"id": 308239, "content": "觉得对自己有用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490019}, {"id": 308240, "content": "至少用过一次，为了避免再要用的情况留在手机里，比如office套件，一些小工具", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490015}, {"id": 308241, "content": "下了一堆学习英语的软件，用了不到一天就都弃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419395}, {"id": 309009, "content": "大概是容量用不完，来充数", "image": "img/option/option/20181106133412bQPaLoXMSVUenxys.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454751}, {"id": 308242, "content": "额，你信吗", "image": "img/option/option/201811020027544GXt0V1qfEUp9yZR.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182917}, {"id": 308754, "content": "学校强制下载真是相当恶心了，软件垃圾不说，还得强迫自己用下去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460807}, {"id": 308243, "content": "没有稳定梯子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470298}, {"id": 308245, "content": "限免", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 308246, "content": "假装自己热爱学习 下载了一堆学习什么的APP 最后刷QQ微博就完了那些APP", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180833}, {"id": 308247, "content": "觉得下了这些“有态度”的app 觉得能改变自己\n\n现在想想真是给这些app太大压力了 (´･_･`)", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487446}, {"id": 311068, "content": "一堆英语学习app，最后打开的只有日报。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315794}, {"id": 317724, "content": "海外全家桶", "image": "img/option/option/20181220091610M19DFUTh5tbszJG4", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147315}, {"id": 308253, "content": "限时打折就得不错，想不起来用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870229}, {"id": 326941, "content": "怎么点开细看啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580649}, {"id": 308511, "content": "广告推荐来的 手机内存太大懒得删", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489238}, {"id": 308771, "content": "一堆拍照修图的app最后只用b612和vsco", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 308517, "content": "朋友推荐的落网，很喜欢用。\n后来朋友去世，没再用了，也没删。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456319}, {"id": 309031, "content": "下载时想用但是没机会用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494577}, {"id": 308266, "content": "每次总想找一个简单的浏览器，谁知道，下载下来，一点用都没有还不如原来的浏览器，又卸载，把原来的浏览器下载回来。。。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457732}, {"id": 315690, "content": "本想下一个背单词的软件，接着蹦出了英语阅读，开心词场，双语翻译官，旅行阅读，不看也不想删", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 308779, "content": "关于学习的软件呵都发霉了呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493072}, {"id": 308524, "content": "易班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490831}, {"id": 310065, "content": "诗经", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496369}, {"id": 308787, "content": "限免App，总有一天可以用上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363478}, {"id": 308276, "content": "以前用过觉得很好玩但是装了就不会主动点开...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659826}, {"id": 308788, "content": "很多游戏玩腻了就不玩了，但又舍不得删。比如水果忍者，Temple Run，Candy Crush", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471871}, {"id": 310069, "content": "别人推荐的吧\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499180}, {"id": 309048, "content": "这个软件到底怎么用？", "image": "img/option/option/20181106151005eWkd9bKVEZj56tLh.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494773}, {"id": 308538, "content": "当我想着我明天一定要学英语的时候：外研随身学，星火英语，百词斩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490919}]}